    # A "Bye [persistent.dad], be safe..."
    A "Adiós [persistent.dad], cuídate..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:788
translate spanish d5f_b113e38b:

    # "You make your way to Old Cairo..."
    "Te diriges hacia el Viejo Cairo..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:793
translate spanish d5f_22aa4db4:

    # Zt "Let's hope [Ki] and [Ko]'s death wasn't traced to me..."
    Zt "Esperemos que las muertes de [Ki] y [Ko] no se remonten a mí..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:794
translate spanish d5f_08063d09:

    # Zt "...only one way to find out, I guess."
    Zt "... solo hay una manera de averiguarlo, supongo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:796
translate spanish d5f_35b475d1:

    # Zt "I should go visit [Ki] and [Ko], if they're home."
    Zt "Debería visitar a [Ki] y [Ko], si están en casa."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:799
translate spanish d5f_a41589a5:

    # Zt "Why is the door open..."
    Zt "¿Por qué está la puerta abierta...?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:802
translate spanish d5f_2d57f05a:

    # Zt "Hmm..."
    Zt "Hmm..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:805
translate spanish d5f_bb8807d4:

    # "{i}You read the notes in the book..."
    "{i}Lees las notas del libro..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:806
translate spanish d5f_9faacb5f:

    # No "Shaqiq, you know the deal."
    No "Shaqiq, ya conoces el acuerdo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:807
translate spanish d5f_2b158385:

    # No "We're heading back to the Citadel to continue working from there."
    No "Volvemos a la Ciudadela para seguir trabajando desde allí."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:808
translate spanish d5f_83119b49:

    # No "Go to the inner city, the former banking district. From there, head west."
    No "Ve al centro de la ciudad, al antiguo distrito bancario. Desde allí, dirígete al oeste."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:809
translate spanish d5f_b5ffb40b:

    # No "List of items: Fuel cans: 4, tires: 2, - the box with mechanical parts"
    No "Lista de artículos: Bidones de combustible: 4, neumáticos: 2, - la caja con piezas mecánicas"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:810
translate spanish d5f_78d97b6d:

    # No "Important: Remind me to take these notes with me!"
    No "Importante: ¡Recuérdame que me lleve estas notas!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:811
translate spanish d5f_b87ae2a4:

    # Zt "Great, they took off."
    Zt "Genial, se largaron."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:812
translate spanish d5f_9455d835:

    # Zt "I've never heard of the Citadel, but if that's where they actually refine the fuel, I should try my luck and see if I can find it."
    Zt "Nunca había oído hablar de la Ciudadela, pero si allí es donde refinan el combustible, debería intentar mi suerte e intentar encontrarla."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:829
translate spanish d5f_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:833
translate spanish d5f_b24f1e8e:

    # "{i}You eventually arrive at your destination..."
    "{i}Finalmente llegas a tu destino..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:836
translate spanish d5f_b61bab6f:

    # Zt "I don't think I've ever been here before."
    Zt "No creo haber estado aquí antes."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:837
translate spanish d5f_11a8f60f:

    # Zt "The inner city of Old Cairo is too dangerous to hang around for long, even for Stalkers."
    Zt "La ciudad interior del Viejo Cairo es demasiado peligrosa para quedarse mucho tiempo, incluso para los Acechadores."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:840
translate spanish d5f_721761c2:

    # Zt "No wonder the decayed have chosen to build a base in here."
    Zt "No es de extrañar que los Decaídos hayan elegido construir una base aquí."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:841
translate spanish d5f_f493e5d2:

    # Dec "What do you want?"
    Dec "¿Qué quieres?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:844
translate spanish d5f_8bb0b03e:

    # Dec "Speak, stranger!"
    Dec "¡Habla, forastero!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:847
translate spanish d5f_7eaa7e92:

    # Z "I usually find your people in the city outskirts."
    Z "Suelo encontrar a tu gente en las afueras de la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:848
translate spanish d5f_a8fa86d7:

    # Z "I have an agreement with them, and I was expecting to get some fuel."
    Z "Tengo un acuerdo con ellos, y esperaba conseguir algo de combustible."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:849
translate spanish d5f_83a68720:

    # Z "Except, when I got there, all I found were the notes that lead me here. Have you people abandoned the outpost?"
    Z "Excepto que cuando llegué allí, lo único que encontré fueron las notas que me llevaron aquí. ¿Acaso vuestra gente ha abandonado el puesto avanzado?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:852
translate spanish d5f_d978bde1:

    # Dec "You weren't supposed to find us."
    Dec "Se supone que no debías encontrarnos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:853
translate spanish d5f_6e02cb1a:

    # Z "Then you should have done a better job at hiding your tracks."
    Z "Entonces deberíais haber hecho un mejor trabajo ocultando vuestras huellas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:854
translate spanish d5f_b4a4dfb4:

    # Dec "Even so, whatever deal you had, whoever you had it with, the deal does not exist anymore."
    Dec "Aun así, sea cual sea el trato que tenías, con quien sea que lo tuvieras, el trato ya no existe."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:855
translate spanish d5f_c288934a:

    # Z "This looks like a place you'd rather keep a secret. I can ensure it stays that way, but I do need fuel."
    Z "Esto parece un lugar que preferirías mantener en secreto. Puedo asegurarme de que siga así, pero necesito combustible."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:856
translate spanish d5f_bf980f9b:

    # Dec "Fine! I'm just a guard. You will have to sort it out with the people inside. Go speak with our traders..."
    Dec "¡Bien! Sólo soy un guardia. Tendrás que arreglarlo con la gente de dentro. Ve a hablar con nuestros comerciantes..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:857
translate spanish d5f_2e2e7961:

    # Dec "See if you can convince them not to serve you up for dinner instead."
    Dec "A ver si puedes convencerles de que no te sirvan la cena en su lugar."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:858
translate spanish d5f_3222bf0b:

    # Dec "I'm warning you, though: no funny business, or you really will end up on a plate, before you even get to say your piece."
    Dec "Te advierto, sin embargo: nada de cosas graciosas, o realmente acabarás en un plato antes de siquiera tener la oportunidad de decir lo que piensas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:859
translate spanish d5f_5ab3574d_2:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:862
translate spanish d5f_2c2fbbbb:

    # "{i}You are let through..."
    "{i}Te dejan pasar..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:865
translate spanish d5f_8f4d8113:

    # "{i}You hear voices in the distance..."
    "{i}Oyes voces en la distancia..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:866
translate spanish d5f_ec7c0282:

    # Dec "When did they arrive?"
    Dec "¿Cuándo han llegado?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:867
translate spanish d5f_15043a18:

    # Dec "Yesterday."
    Dec "Ayer."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:868
translate spanish d5f_4b61aee7:

    # Dec "It was a small group; only a couple of them fought back."
    Dec "Era un grupo pequeño; sólo un par de ellos se defendieron."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:869
translate spanish d5f_12abe2ff:

    # Dec "We killed those and captured the other three."
    Dec "Matamos a aquellos y capturamos a los otros tres."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:872
translate spanish d5f_04adca67:

    # Dec "What do you want with them?"
    Dec "¿Qué quieres hacer con ellos?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:873
translate spanish d5f_d722b4e6:

    # Dec "Let's see..."
    Dec "Veamos..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:876
translate spanish d5f_3254ce94:

    # Dec "This girl will work in processing ."
    Dec "Esta chica trabajará en el procesamiento."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:877
translate spanish d5f_a0ab8594:

    # Dec "Good idea, she seems to be in enough of a good shape to work."
    Dec "Buena idea, parece que está en buena forma para trabajar."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:880
translate spanish d5f_bf828a14:

    # C "{i}*sobbing*"
    C "{i}*sollozando*"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:881
translate spanish d5f_aaf759a5:

    # Dec "Get the fat one to the butchers."
    Dec "Lleva al gordo a la carnicería"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:882
translate spanish d5f_c2a9a3ff:

    # Dec "The sick one, that one on the left..."
    Dec "El enfermo, el de la izquierda..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:883
translate spanish d5f_5dc1f720:

    # Dec "Try to break him. He is already turning."
    Dec "Intenta doblegarlo. Ya se está convirtiendo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:884
translate spanish d5f_de88a466:

    # Dec "Yes, good."
    Dec "Sí, bien."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:885
translate spanish d5f_5ab3574d_3:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:888
translate spanish d5f_16322f8f:

    # Dec "This is the one..."
    Dec "Este es el..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:889
translate spanish d5f_57c8eefb:

    # Zt "...?"
    Zt "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:892
translate spanish d5f_03c8bb75:

    # Dec "Get in, slaves."
    Dec "Entren, esclavos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:893
translate spanish d5f_30ed63ef:

    # Dec "You're going to work in the refinery, hrhr."
    Dec "Tú vas a trabajar en la refinería, jejeje."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:894
translate spanish d5f_8fb66230:

    # Zt "These trains are running..."
    Zt "Estos trenes están funcionando..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:895
translate spanish d5f_892d1339:

    # Zt "This must be how they connect to the refineries outside of Cairo..."
    Zt "Esto debe ser como se conectan con las refinerías fuera del Viejo Cairo..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:897
translate spanish d5f_c8931520:

    # C2 "Where are you going?"
    C2 "¿Adónde vas?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:899
translate spanish d5f_a5d746bf:

    # Z "...!"
    Z "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:902
translate spanish d5f_3c578e4f:

    # C2 "I have not seen you here before."
    C2 "No te he visto antes por aquí."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:903
translate spanish d5f_68c32069:

    # C2 "And I don't like you nosing around."
    C2 "Y no me gusta que husmeen."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:906
translate spanish d5f_6337c0de:

    # C2 "What are you looking for, anyway?"
    C2 "¿Qué estás buscando, de todos modos?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:907
translate spanish d5f_4df09d7c:

    # Z "I'm here to buy fuel. I was told to come inside, but nothing else."
    Z "He venido a comprar combustible. Me han dicho que entre, pero nada más."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:911
translate spanish d5f_271b6fce:

    # C2 "..."
    C2 "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:912
translate spanish d5f_1aa1ecd8:

    # C2 "Follow me..."
    C2 "Sígueme..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:916
translate spanish d5f_c8931520_1:

    # C2 "Where are you going?"
    C2 "¿Adónde vas?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:918
translate spanish d5f_a5d746bf_1:

    # Z "...!"
    Z "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:921
translate spanish d5f_d9fa8bdd:

    # Ki "Hopefully you're not leaving already, Master [persistent.player_name]!"
    Ki "¡Espero que no te vayas ya, Amo [persistent.player_name]!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:922
translate spanish d5f_d09f8dfb:

    # Ko "Yeah, we told you we would owe you one, hrhrhr."
    Ko "Sí, te dijimos que te debíamos una, jejeje."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:923
translate spanish d5f_65f994c3:

    # Zt "Great..."
    Zt "Genial..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:924
translate spanish d5f_700af1ec:

    # Z "[Ki], [Ko]! I see you guys made it here in one piece."
    Z "¡[Ki], [Ko]! Veo que habéis llegado de una pieza."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:927
translate spanish d5f_0df37a5b:

    # Ko "What do you mean in one piece?"
    Ko "¿Qué quieres decir con\"de una pieza'?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:928
translate spanish d5f_acf275d6:

    # Ko "That trip was easy, and our new home is pretty awesome as well!"
    Ko "Ese viaje fue fácil, ¡y nuestro nuevo hogar también es bastante impresionante!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:929
translate spanish d5f_95e9f5ae:

    # Ki "Yeah, indeed it is, hrhrhr."
    Ki "Sí, efectivamente es así, jejeje."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:930
translate spanish d5f_c06cba9b:

    # Ko "Glad to see you're finally visiting us."
    Ko "Me alegro de que por fin nos visites."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:931
translate spanish d5f_77001ff0:

    # Ko "Why don't we show you our new little place, what do you say?"
    Ko "¿Por qué no le enseñamos nuestro nuevo lugar, qué dices?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:932
translate spanish d5f_41c71c3a:

    # Ki "Yeah, what do you say?"
    Ki "Sí, ¿qué dices?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:933
translate spanish d5f_87f9eb24:

    # Z "Sure... I'm here looking for some fuel, but that can wait I guess."
    Z "Claro... Estoy aquí buscando algo de combustible, pero eso puede esperar, supongo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:934
translate spanish d5f_dfa6962f:

    # Ko "Hrhr, yes... Yes it can! Follow us!"
    Ko "Jejeje, sí... ¡Sí que se puede! ¡Síguenos!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:939
translate spanish d5f_eab43324:

    # Ko "I hope you're having fun with that elf we sold you."
    Ko "Espero que te estés divirtiendo con la elfo que te vendimos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:940
translate spanish d5f_b73924a8:

    # Ki "Yeah, such a shame. But that artifact you gave us, oh boy."
    Ki "Sí, es una pena. Pero ese artefacto que nos diste, oh chico."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:941
translate spanish d5f_86d0ba5b:

    # Ko "Oh boy!"
    Ko "¡Oh chico!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:942
translate spanish d5f_73adc345:

    # Ki "We got some good stuff for that!"
    Ki "¡Tenemos un buen material para eso!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:943
translate spanish d5f_02fba05f:

    # Z "Good stuff? Anything I might be interested in?"
    Z "¿Cosas buenas? ¿Algo que pueda interesarme?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:944
translate spanish d5f_56744eaa:

    # Ki "Food, gadgets, and more traps, more of those collars, hrhrhr!"
    Ki "Comida, artilugios y más trampas, más de esos collares, ¡jejeje!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:946
translate spanish d5f_d038558e:

    # Ko "Let me tell you, [persistent.player_name]."
    Ko "Deja que te diga, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:947
translate spanish d5f_3ee3f353:

    # Ko "That elf tasted d-e-l-i-c-i-o-u-s."
    Ko "Esa elfo sabía d-e-l-i-c-i-o-s-a."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:948
translate spanish d5f_78be6598:

    # Ki "Yeah, I have never eaten so well before."
    Ki "Sí, nunca había comido tan bien."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:949
translate spanish d5f_14714386:

    # Ko "This way, Master [persistent.player_name]."
    Ko "Por aquí, Amo [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:950
translate spanish d5f_9b78d624:

    # Ko "You will be impressed with our new digs!"
    Ko "Quedarás impresionado con nuestras nuevas excavaciones."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:951
translate spanish d5f_8beb25d1:

    # Ki "Yeah, hrhr, it's right next to the main hall!"
    Ki "Sí, jejeje, ¡está al lado del salón principal!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:952
translate spanish d5f_5ab3574d_4:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:953
translate spanish d5f_51e70326:

    # Z "Are you serious...?"
    Z "¿Hablas en serio...?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:957
translate spanish d5f_c0da793d:

    # Ko "So..."
    Ko "Así que..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:960
translate spanish d5f_d7521830:

    # Ko "...what do you say?"
    Ko "... ¿qué dices?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:965
translate spanish d5f_2519a059:

    # Z "It's a toilet."
    Z "Es un aseo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:966
translate spanish d5f_29b2376a:

    # Z "You're living in a toilet."
    Z "Estáis viviendo en un aseo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:969
translate spanish d5f_5e5a274f:

    # Ko "Not just any toilet, na na!"
    Ko "No es un aseo cualquiera, ¡nada de eso!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:970
translate spanish d5f_fe97e006:

    # Ki "Indeed, not just any!"
    Ki "En efecto, ¡no es cualquiera!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:971
translate spanish d5f_c3745d70:

    # Ko "This is where the boss goes."
    Ko "Aquí es donde va el jefe."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:972
translate spanish d5f_a943f9c6:

    # Ko "The big boss."
    Ko "El gran jefe."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:973
translate spanish d5f_0701f33e:

    # Ki "Technically, we're charged with the maintenance, with keeping the plumbing going, hrhr!"
    Ki "Técnicamente, estamos encargados del mantenimiento, de mantener las cañerías en funcionamiento, ¡jejeje!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:974
translate spanish d5f_5ab3574d_5:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:978
translate spanish d5f_1a749e5b:

    # Z "It's... practical, I guess?"
    Z "Es... práctico, supongo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:981
translate spanish d5f_0604d00e:

    # Ko "Oh, it is!"
    Ko "Oh, sí lo es."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:982
translate spanish d5f_9d9f2ef2:

    # Ki "It is indeed!"
    Ki "¡Así es, en efecto!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:983
translate spanish d5f_0a0f7337:

    # Ko "Sure, it doesn't smell nice..."
    Ko "Claro, no huele bien..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:984
translate spanish d5f_5a797ea0:

    # Ko "...but we are in Old Cairo, so not like it smells good anywhere, hrhr!"
    Ko "¡...pero estamos en el Viejo Cairo, así que no huele bien en ningún sitio, jejeje!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:985
translate spanish d5f_5ab3574d_6:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:989
translate spanish d5f_a987c21c:

    # Z "You guys are disgusting."
    Z "Sois unos asquerosos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:990
translate spanish d5f_34cf084a:

    # Z "I knew you guys were filthy, but this is a new level."
    Z "Sabía que erais unos asquerosos, pero esto ya es otro nivel."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:991
translate spanish d5f_65869e37:

    # Z "I'm almost impressed, really."
    Z "Estoy casi impresionado, de verdad."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:994
translate spanish d5f_f8fd1c30:

    # Ko "If you weren't such a good friend we would probably have you for dinner for what you said."
    Ko "Si no fueras tan buen amigo probablemente te invitaríamos a cenar por lo que has dicho."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:995
translate spanish d5f_1454d475:

    # Ki "Hrhrhr."
    Ki "Jejejeje."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:996
translate spanish d5f_0b8d49b7:

    # Ki "But he is kind of right..."
    Ki "Pero él tiene algo de razón..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:997
translate spanish d5f_addc09c3:

    # Ko "I guess..."
    Ko "Supongo..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:998
translate spanish d5f_b44bbd2a:

    # Z "That, and you know I could kill you both without breaking a sweat..."
    Z "Eso, y sabes que podría mataros a los dos sin despeinarme..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:999
translate spanish d5f_adad0748:

    # Ki "Well.. You don't have to put it that way..."
    Ki "Bueno... No hace falta que lo digas así..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:1003
translate spanish d5f_fairy_1c4c2ee8:

    # Z "If you excuse me..."
    Z "Si me perdonáis..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:1004
translate spanish d5f_fairy_5b649c06:

    # Z "It was a long journey, and since I'm here, I bet your boss won't mind sharing the toilet..."
    Z "Fue un largo viaje, y ya que estoy aquí, apuesto a que a tu jefe no le importará compartir el baño..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:1005
