# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6121
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_9c1c70ba:

    # Fa "But just because she trusts you doesn't mean that I have to share her blind faith."
    Fa "Pero que ella confíe en ti no significa que yo tenga que compartir su fe ciega."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6122
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_2803e965:

    # Fa "See, in time we have come to follow her instincts and respect that she knows what she's doing, but we've been burned, occasionally."
    Fa "Verás, con el tiempo hemos llegado a seguir sus instintos y respetar que sabe lo que hace, pero hemos salido quemados, ocasionalmente."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6123
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_021b21f8:

    # Fa "So, I will keep an eye on you. I don't know who you are, yet... but I know what you are not!"
    Fa "Así que, te estaré vigilando. No sé quién eres aún... ¡pero sé lo que no eres!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6126
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_503467bc:

    # Fa "...and if I see the smallest hint of treachery towards my people here..."
    Fa "... y si veo el más mínimo indicio de traición hacia mi pueblo aquí..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6129
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_15557b98:

    # Fa "...you are fucked, you got that? I. Will. End. You."
    Fa "... estás jodido, ¿te enteras? Te. Voy. A. Destrozar."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6134
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_9e79131e:

    # Fa "[I] and I will show you around, now."
    Fa "[I] y yo te mostraremos el lugar, ahora."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6137
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_3b4dec8a:

    # Fa "Are you ready?"
    Fa "¿Estás preparado?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6138
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_7450ad4e:

    # "You decide to play along for now..."
    "Decides seguir el juego por ahora..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6139
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_d99fb79e:

    # Z "Lead the way."
    Z "Tú primero."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6142
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_f115da6b:

    # Fa "That's what I like to hear..."
    Fa "Eso es lo que me gusta oír..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6145
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_d4c7bdbc:

    # Fa "Watch your step."
    Fa "Cuidado con lo que dices."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6148
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_dd181364:

    # Fa "Welcome to our secret place..."
    Fa "Bienvenido a nuestro lugar secreto..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6149
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_ba3c1d3f:

    # Fa "We found this bunker a year ago."
    Fa "Encontramos este búnker hace un año."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6150
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_77f8bd12:

    # Fa "Getting in here was tougher than you might think..."
    Fa "Entrar aquí fue más duro de lo que crees..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6151
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_de529808:

    # Fa "But it was worth it."
    Fa "Pero ha merecido la pena."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6152
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_a9a21833:

    # Fa "Functioning water filtration systems, stainless military equipment from way back, and... well, look around..."
    Fa "Sistemas de filtración de agua funcionando, equipo militar inoxidable de hace años, y... bueno, mira a tu alrededor..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6153
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_0db1cefd:

    # Fa "The only problem is the extreme scarcity of resources."
    Fa "El único problema es la extrema escasez de recursos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6156
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_e3004d69:

    # C2 "...a quick reminder before we begin the training."
    C2 "... un rápido recordatorio antes de comenzar el entrenamiento."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6159
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_cfe030b2:

    # C2 "That body armour you're equipped with is in limited supply, so treat it like it's your second skin."
    C2 "Esa armadura corporal con la que estáis equipadas tiene un suministro limitado, así que trátarla como si fuera vuestra segunda piel."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6160
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_fc527b1e:

    # C3 "Yes, ma'am!"
    C3 "Sí, señora."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6163
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_ba241e5c:

    # Fa "Our engineers and scientists are doing the best they can to keep this place running..."
    Fa "Nuestros ingenieros y científicos están haciendo lo mejor que pueden para mantener este lugar en funcionamiento..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6164
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_c6f334c6:

    # Fa "Most of what we know is self taught; based on information stolen from the Queen's library, found here, or scavenged from the old world."
    Fa "La mayoría de lo que sabemos es autodidacta; basado en información robada de la biblioteca de la Reina, encontrada aquí, o saqueada del viejo mundo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6167
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_19bc9fa5:

    # Fa "The capacity of this bunker is limited."
    Fa "La capacidad de este búnker es limitada."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6168
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_d668691b:

    # Fa "So in a way it's good that there are only a couple dozen of us."
    Fa "Así que, de alguna forma, es bueno que solo seamos unas pocas docenas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6171
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_a1f6475d:

    # Fa "But this is not where our road ends...our numbers will rise in time."
    Fa "Pero aquí no termina nuestro camino... Nuestro número aumentará con el tiempo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6174
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_7f45e2dc:

    # Fa "Eventually, we will have to find a way to call Zeta our new home, not just a place where we are abused and killed...."
    Fa "Al final, tendremos que encontrar la manera de llamar a Zeta nuestro nuevo hogar, no sólo un lugar donde nos maltrata y nos matan...."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6177
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6180
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_da559b98:

    # Fa "Let me show you our lab... [I], you can go."
    Fa "Déjame mostrarte nuestro laboratorio... [I], puedes irte."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6181
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_6e8dfb5c:

    # Fa "Thank you for your service today, and welcome back."
    Fa "Gracias por tu servicio de hoy, y bienvenida de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6189
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_4e6bd477:

    # Fa "This is our laboratory."
    Fa "Este es nuestro laboratorio."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6190
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_e3d911f2:

    # Fa "Don't ask me about it. I couldn't tell you anything beyond what you can see for yourself."
    Fa "No me preguntes al respecto. No podría decirte nada más allá de lo que puedes ver por ti mismo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6193
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_4ddfc021:

    # Fa "...and yes, we found it in this exact state. Stainless steel, working bulbs and machines... all that stuff."
    Fa "... y sí, lo encontramos exactamente en este estado. Acero inoxidable, bombillas y máquinas funcionando... todo eso."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6194
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_20e39289:

    # Fa "There are no traces of who built this, but their methods were advanced, to say the least."
    Fa "No hay rastros de quién construyó esto, pero sus métodos eran avanzados, por decir lo menos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6197
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_ff22e943:

    # Fa "[Pe] mostly works here alone, you can ask her all the specifics. Not that I expect you'll understand them."
    Fa "[Pe] la mayoría de las veces trabaja aquí sola, puedes preguntarle todos los detalles. No es que espere que los entiendas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6200
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_58147e0d:

    # Zt "I have never seen anything like this. For such an ancient facility to exist, in such a state of conservation and..."
    Zt "Nunca había visto algo como esto. Para que una instalación tan antigua exista, en tal estado de conservación y..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6203
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_7b6ef5e7:

    # Fa "[Pe], I was told you were asking for me."
    Fa "[Pe], me han dicho que preguntabas por mí."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6206
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_e521b145:

    # Fa "How are you doing with the probes?"
    Fa "¿Cómo te va con las sondas?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6209
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_b0c11803:

    # "She moves towards her..."
    "Se acerca a ella..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6210
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_c93ace46:

    # Pe "Commander. I waited for hours."
    Pe "Comandante. He esperado durante horas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6211
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_5b0ba8ff:

    # Fa "I know I'm late, but [I] brought someone new, as you can see."
    Fa "Llegué tarde, pero traje a alguien nuevo, como puedes ver."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6214
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_af646e49:

    # Pe "Can he be trusted?"
    Pe "¿Se puede confiar en él?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6217
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_b1a4b19d:

    # Fa "Well... how do I explain it?"
    Fa "Bueno... ¿cómo te lo explico?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6218
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_f6da1784:

    # Fa "[I] trusts him; I don't. At least not yet. He will have to prove himself, like everybody else."
    Fa "[I] confía en él; yo no. Al menos, todavía no. Tendrá que probarse, como todos los demás."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6219
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_9f9ef78e:

    # Fa "Anyway, you can go to the barracks now, I'm done with the tour."
    Fa "De todos modos, puedes ir a los barracones ahora, ya terminé con el recorrido."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6222
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_d9e6d47c:

    # Fa "See if you find [I]. She might show you a place to sleep."
    Fa "Ve si encuentras a [I]. Podría mostrarte un lugar donde dormir."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6223
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_a27120dc:

    # Fa "It's getting late, and I assume you don't want to find your way back to wherever you came from in the dark."
    Fa "Se está haciendo tarde, y supongo que no querrás encontrar el camino de regreso a donde viniste en la oscuridad."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6226
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_752b0a84:

    # Pe "Commander, I-"
    Pe "Comandante, yo..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6229
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_c6fcdf23:

    # Fa "Shh... whatever it is, it can wait until he's gone."
    Fa "Shh... lo que sea, puede esperar hasta que se haya ido."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6232
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_f2c7ebc9:

    # Faw "Cute little thing. Always coming up with more problems..."
    Faw "Cosita linda. Siempre inventando más problemas..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6235
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_a86ed323:

    # Fa "As I said, that's it from me. We will talk more later."
    Fa "Como dije, eso es todo de mi parte. Hablaremos más tarde."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6238
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_de97941f:

    # Fa "What? Are you jealous? There's the door, bye!"
    Fa "¿Qué? ¿Estás celosa? ¡Ahí está la puerta, adiós!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6241
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_979e775b:

    # Z "{i}*chuckles*{/i} Interesting."
    Z "{i}*risilla*{/i} Interesante."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6245
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_5eeb2345:

    # "You leave..."
    "Te vas..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6246
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_77352daa:

    # Fa "Now... tell me again slowly. I might have a personal task for you after..."
    Fa "Ahora... dime de nuevo lentamente. Podría tener una tarea personal para ti después..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6250
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_605877d2:

    # "{i}You reach the barracks..."
    "{i}Llegas a los barracones..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6255
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6261
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6264
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_cff249ad:

    # "She points to a locker next to one of the beds."
    "Señala un casillero al lado de una de las camas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6267
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_005e9534:

    # Zt "This must have been assigned to me..."
    Zt "Esto debe haberme sido asignado..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6270
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_0b94ef0a:

    # Zt "I guess I should prepare for the night."
    Zt "Supongo que debería prepararme para la noche."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6279
translate spanish ivyzbunker1_33a46fdf:

    # "Some time later..."
    "Pasado un tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6285
translate spanish d5b53_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6289
translate spanish d5b53_285f519a:

    # "You lay in bed, processing the events of today."
    "Te acuestas en la cama, procesando los eventos del día."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6290
translate spanish d5b53_291531f3:

    # "The elf you saved from the hands of the Decayed... She had lingered at the edge of your mind, but you hadn't thought much of it. You certainly did not expect that event to lead to setting foot into this incredible place."
    "La elfa que salvaste de las manos de los Podridos... Ella se había quedado en el borde de tus pensamientos, pero no habías pensado mucho en ello. Desde luego, no esperabas que ese evento te llevara a poner un pie en este lugar increíble."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6291
translate spanish d5b53_c5fcc791:

    # "{i}What makes the desert beautiful is that somewhere it hides a well.{/i}... the ancient quote your master used to recite, resonates in your mind, unbidden but never so appropriate."
    "{i}Lo que hace al desierto hermoso es que en algún lugar esconde un pozo.{/i}... La antigua cita que solía recitar tu maestro resuena en tu mente, inesperada pero tan apropiada."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6297
translate spanish d5b53_c158fd95:

    # Zt "Hm...?"
    Zt "¿Hm...?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6300
translate spanish d5b53_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6301
