translate spanish fangsqanda_6ba31a27:

    # Fa "Doesn't matter where you are. In Egypt or other countries, it's the same story everywhere."
    Fa "No importa dónde estés. En Egipto o en otros países, es la misma historia en todas partes."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6996
translate spanish fangsqanda_acd0b677:

    # Fa "Mutants like us are either enslaved, hunted down or worse, served for dinner..."
    Fa "Los mutantes como nosotros son esclavizados, perseguidos o, peor aún, servidos como cena..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6997
translate spanish fangsqanda_7d9ff97e:

    # Fa "We can often avoid the decayed, as they mostly hide in the ruins of Old Cairo."
    Fa "A menudo podemos evitar a los decaídos, ya que la mayoría se esconden en las ruinas del Viejo Cairo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6998
translate spanish fangsqanda_62c5e398:

    # Fa "And raiders are a plague to everyone..."
    Fa "Y los asaltantes son una plaga para todos..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:6999
translate spanish fangsqanda_c0306e1a:

    # Fa "But the Queen and her patrols... your so called civilization.. They're just as bad."
    Fa "Pero la Reina y sus patrullas... su llamada civilización.. Son igual de malos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7002
translate spanish fangsqanda_84419846:

    # Fa "Zeta is our biggest oppressor at this moment."
    Fa "Zeta es nuestro mayor opresor en este momento."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7003
translate spanish fangsqanda_1e3ad3c7:

    # Z "What are your plans to solve the situation?"
    Z "¿Cuáles son tus planes para resolver la situación?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7004
translate spanish fangsqanda_32c5e99a:

    # Fa "We plan to infiltrate Zeta and take down the Queen."
    Fa "Planeamos infiltrarnos en Zeta y acabar con la Reina."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7007
translate spanish fangsqanda_8f7ecc27:

    # Fa "Don't look at me like that, you moron! I'm joking! We're not stupid."
    Fa "No me mires así, imbécil. ¡Que te estoy vacilando! No somos idiotas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7008
translate spanish fangsqanda_617a8d6e:

    # Fa "All we want is equal rights and recognition. We're trying to figure out a path towards that."
    Fa "Lo único que queremos es la igualdad de derechos y el reconocimiento. Estamos tratando de encontrar un camino hacia eso."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7009
translate spanish fangsqanda_ed489724:

    # Fa "Jokes aside, we want to obtain it peacefully, but we must also defend our lives and learn how to fight with what we've got."
    Fa "Bromas aparte, queremos conseguirlo pacíficamente, pero también debemos defender nuestras vidas y aprender a luchar con lo que tenemos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7010
translate spanish fangsqanda_4d04d235:

    # Fa "We are few. We have a few talents but that doesn't mean I want a war against Zeta or your queen; unless she forces us in a corner."
    Fa "Somos pocos. Tenemos pocos talentos, pero eso no significa que quiera una guerra contra Zeta o su reina; a menos que nos obligue a acorralarnos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7011
translate spanish fangsqanda_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7012
translate spanish fangsqanda_8ad8e5d2:

    # Fa "We're not entirely desperate; at least, those of us who have found our way to this haven."
    Fa "No estamos del todo desesperados; al menos, los que hemos encontrado el camino hacia este refugio."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7013
translate spanish fangsqanda_f845f2ee:

    # Fa "But if it comes down to it, we will do what we must, to protect our own. Isolation is not an option, when resources are so limited."
    Fa "Pero si llega el caso, haremos lo que debamos, para proteger a los nuestros. El aislamiento no es una opción, cuando los recursos son tan limitados."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7018
translate spanish fangsqanda_7ce27e45:

    # Z "Do you trust me?"
    Z "¿Confías en mí?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7021
translate spanish fangsqanda_1154c318:

    # Fa "Fuck, no!"
    Fa "¡Joder, no!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7022
translate spanish fangsqanda_dde31871:

    # Fa "Let me put it this way..."
    Fa "Déjame ponerlo de esta manera..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7023
translate spanish fangsqanda_eb0116f0:

    # Fa "I know not all Desert Stalkers out there are Zetan citizens or loyal to the city. Many prefer to stay neutral and dip their fingers in many different jars."
    Fa "Sé que no todos los Acechadores del Desierto son ciudadanos zetanos o leales a la ciudad. Muchos prefieren mantenerse neutrales y meter los dedos en muchos frascos diferentes."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7024
translate spanish fangsqanda_99de8549:

    # Fa "You however? Zetan through and through, for all I can tell."
    Fa "Sin embargo, tú... Zetano hasta la médula, por lo que veo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7025
translate spanish fangsqanda_a1eba8ae:

    # Fa "I'm told you even have the queen's ear. She gives you private audiences."
    Fa "Me han dicho que incluso tienes el oído de la reina. Ella te concede audiencias privadas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7029
translate spanish fangsqanda_c67db001:

    # Fa "Don't get me wrong, I like your attitude..."
    Fa "No me malinterpretes, me gusta tu actitud..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7030
translate spanish fangsqanda_cf6a0e45:

    # Fa "And you were a great fuck."
    Fa "Y tú has sido un gran polvo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7031
translate spanish fangsqanda_503d46fb:

    # Fa "But that's not enough to win my trust..."
    Fa "Pero eso no es suficiente para ganar mi confianza..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7032
translate spanish fangsqanda_ac69d2e8:

    # Fa "The lives of my sisters and brothers depend on me and on my judgement."
    Fa "Las vidas de mis hermanas y hermanos dependen de mí y de mi juicio."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7036
translate spanish fangsqanda_c67db001_1:

    # Fa "Don't get me wrong, I like your attitude..."
    Fa "No me malinterpretes, me gusta tu actitud..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7037
translate spanish fangsqanda_991680e4:

    # Fa "But I need more than that to be convinced..."
    Fa "Pero necesito más que eso para convencerme..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7038
translate spanish fangsqanda_6440f93e:

    # Fa "The lives of my sisters and brothers depend on it."
    Fa "La vida de mis hermanas y hermanos depende de ello."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7039
translate spanish fangsqanda_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7044
translate spanish fangsqanda_ffcbd703:

    # Z "Tell me more about [I]."
    Z "Cuéntame más sobre [I]."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7047
translate spanish fangsqanda_8bc3db32:

    # Fa "You might as well ask a truth sayer..."
    Fa "También podrías pedirle a una persona que diga la verdad..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7050
translate spanish fangsqanda_bdb49c38:

    # Fa "[I] is one of a kind..."
    Fa "[I] es única..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7051
translate spanish fangsqanda_b6a3d2f8:

    # Fa "I have never seen a mutant like her."
    Fa "Nunca he visto a una mutante como ella."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7052
translate spanish fangsqanda_540364a4:

    # Fa "And I am not talking about the ears of course. plenty of us have those, that's how the whole {i}Elves{/i} thing started."
    Fa "Y no estoy hablando de las orejas, por supuesto. Muchos de nosotros tenemos de esas, así fue como empezó todo el rollo de los {i}Elfos{/i}."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7055
translate spanish fangsqanda_340889cc:

    # Fa "Something about her radiates a mixture of curiosity and wisdom. Her instincts are rarely wrong, and people seem to trust her implicitly."
    Fa "Algo en ella irradia una mezcla de curiosidad y sabiduría. Sus instintos rara vez se equivocan y la gente parece confiar en ella implícitamente."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7056
translate spanish fangsqanda_8315523d:

    # Fa "She doesn't talk, but people follow her, just like you did. I can't explain it, only make it work for me; and only sometimes. It's annoying, really."
    Fa "No habla, pero la gente la sigue, igual que tú. No puedo explicarlo, sólo hacer que me funcione; y sólo a veces. Es molesto, de verdad."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7064
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_e1a67f0f:

    # Z "I noticed that when she looks at you, her eyes turn grey."
    Z "Me he dado cuenta de que cuando te mira, sus ojos se vuelven grises."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7067
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_9a058d8b:

    # Fa "I know that."
    Fa "Lo sé."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7068
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_3fee7ce2:

    # Fa "And everytime she looks at you, they turn green."
    Fa "Y cada vez que te mira a tí, se le ponen verdes."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7069
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_74a20dd7:

    # Fa "Those green eyes... that's how they were when we first met."
    Fa "Esos ojos verdes... así eran cuando nos conocimos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7070
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_8edf6aed:

    # Fa "It's why I gave her the name [I]."
    Fa "Por eso le di el nombre de [I]."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7071
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_e6a43e7a:

    # Fa "I think her eyes reflect her mood. Either she does not agree with our plans, or she dislikes me for some other reason."
    Fa "Creo que sus ojos reflejan su estado de ánimo. O bien no está de acuerdo con nuestros planes, o le desagrado por alguna otra razón."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7074
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_10fb5d5a:

    # Fa "But that's life. Soldiers don't always agree with what you tell them."
    Fa "But that's life. Soldiers don't always agree with what you tell them."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7075
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_8bf2eb25:

    # Fa "That is just how things are."
    Fa "Así son las cosas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7076
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_7f5f5858:

    # Fa "It's just unlucky for her that she cannot hide her disapproval, ha!"
    Fa "Es una mala suerte para ella que no pueda ocultar su desaprobación, ¡ja!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7081
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_eab08f94:

    # Z "I have not yet heard her speak."
    Z "Todavía no la he oído hablar."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7082
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_3925ab28:

    # Z "What is that all about?"
    Z "¿De qué se trata todo eso?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7085
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_4d75fee5:

    # Fa "If I only knew..."
    Fa "Si yo lo supiera..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7086
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_2418919d:

    # Fa "She has not spoken a word since she came here."
    Fa "No ha dicho ni una palabra desde que llegó aquí."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7087
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_460b44a2:

    # Z "Ever?"
    Z "¿Alguna vez?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7090
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_838cd55b:

    # Fa "Ever."
    Fa "Alguna vez."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7091
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_3355ff87:

    # Z "How long has she been with you then?"
    Z "¿Cuánto tiempo lleva con vosotros entonces?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7092
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_01c10e94:

    # Fa "Several months..."
    Fa "Varios meses..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7093
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_aa68e49e:

    # Fa "I quickly learned that she's as agile as a fox, and resourceful."
    Fa "Rápidamente aprendí que es ágil como un zorro y con recursos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7094
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_086e0db3:

    # Fa "So I sent her on missions to lead other mutants to us."
    Fa "Así que la envié a misiones para guiar a otros mutantes hacia nosotros."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7099
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_6bee19b3:

    # Z "I found her in Old Cairo."
    Z "La encontré en el Viejo Cairo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7100
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_561c7007:

    # Z "She'd been captured and almost killed by some Decayed."
    Z "Había sido capturada y casi asesinada por unos Decaídos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7101
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_67d8c62d:

    # Z "How did that happen?"
    Z "¿Cómo ocurrió eso?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7104
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_01387773:

    # Fa "She got what?!"
    Fa "¡¿Qué fue lo que ocurrió?!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7105
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_ae96465a:

    # Fa "That's why she looked like she was almost starving!"
    Fa "¡Por eso parecía que se estaba muriendo de hambre!"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7106
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_9d986bfd:

    # Z "You didn't know?"
    Z "¿No lo sabías?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7107
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_184ec38b:

    # Fa "Of course not! She never says a word, how am I supposed to know?!"
    Fa "Por supuesto que no. Nunca dice una palabra, ¿cómo voy a saberlo?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7110
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_c658eb83:

    # Fa "She was on a mission to verify information about other possible mutant hideouts in the region."
    Fa "Estaba en una misión para verificar información sobre otros posibles escondites mutantes en la región."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7111
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_ff455301:

    # Fa "[I] didn't come back for several days..."
    Fa "[I] no volvió durante varios días..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7112
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_bcce52b6:

    # Fa "So I just assumed she needed a bit more time. It wasn't the first time she stayed away for several days."
    Fa "Así que supuse que necesitaba un poco más de tiempo. No era la primera vez que se alejaba durante varios días."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7113
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_b34e0975:

    # Fa "So you rescued her?"
    Fa "¿Así que la rescataste?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7115
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_f936a8f3:

    # Z "Yes. I had to kill both of the decayed holding her hostage."
    Z "Sí. Tuve que matar a los dos decaídos que la tenían como rehén."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7116
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_c1debce7:

    # Z "They weren't letting her go."
    Z "No la dejaban ir."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7119
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_2a2a0377:

    # Fa "You have contacts with the decayed?"
    Fa "¿Tienes contactos con los decaídos?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7120
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_1d3960de:

    # Z "Something like that, yes."
    Z "Algo así, sí."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7121
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_cb8cbf59:

    # Fa "..."
    Fa "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7122
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_b8e47978:

    # Fa "Well... that explains at least why she picked you out of the names of people we were considering to approach."
    Fa "Bueno... eso al menos explica por qué ella te eligió a ti de entre los nombres de las personas que considerábamos acercarnos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7123
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_cb8cbf59_1:

    # Fa "..."
    Fa "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7125
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_d951fcfc:

    # Z "Yes. I bribed them to hand her over to me."
    Z "Sí. Los soborné para que me la entregaran."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7126
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_af3216e9:

    # Z "I was on a tomb raid before, and had to give up my find, to buy her freedom."
    Z "Antes estuve en un asalto a una tumba y tuve que renunciar a mi hallazgo para comprar su libertad."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7129
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_ba515f08:

    # Fa "I know those artifacts are valuable in your home city."
    Fa "Sé que esos artefactos son valiosos en tu ciudad natal."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7130
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_cba9b888:

    # Fa "I have never understood why..."
    Fa "Nunca he entendido por qué..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7131
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7132
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_b8e47978_1:

    # Fa "Well... that explains at least why she picked you out of the names of people we were considering to approach."
    Fa "Bueno... eso al menos explica por qué ella te eligió a ti de entre los nombres de las personas que considerábamos acercarnos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7133
translate spanish fangsivyquestions_cb8cbf59_2:

    # Fa "..."
    Fa "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7141
translate spanish fangsqandadone_02213e5c:

    # Z "So..."
    Z "Así que..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7142
translate spanish fangsqandadone_ffb877dc:

    # Z "What am I doing here?"
    Z "¿Qué estoy haciendo aquí?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7145
translate spanish fangsqandadone_04040117:

    # Fa "Well.. as I told you, we are looking to obtain recognition and equal rights. To get there, we have to talk with somebody. We can't just walk in and say {i}we're here, deal with it!{/i}"
    Fa "Bien... como te dije, buscamos obtener el reconocimiento y la igualdad de derechos. Para conseguirlo, tenemos que hablar con alguien. No podemos llegar sin más y decir {i}estamos aquí, ¡acéptarlo!{/i}."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7146
translate spanish fangsqandadone_88c240f1:

    # Fa "So we've started to look around, to look for people who would be open to listening, and maybe vouch for us."
    Fa "Así que hemos empezado a mirar a nuestro alrededor, a buscar gente que esté dispuesta a escuchar, y tal vez a responder por nosotros."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7147
translate spanish fangsqandadone_d59faeb2:

    # Fa "We have collected some information about notable individuals."
    Fa "Hemos reunido información sobre individuos notables."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7148
translate spanish fangsqandadone_8caac564:

    # Fa "You were one of them. A Stalker, so, hopefully open minded, but also well connected."
    Fa "Tú eras uno de ellos. Un Acechador, así que, esperemos que tenga la mente abierta, pero también bien conectada."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7149
translate spanish fangsqandadone_4a135f8f:

    # Fa "And... as I've just learned, you're a good fighter, and even more connected than we knew."
    Fa "Y... como acabo de descubrir, eres un buen luchador, e incluso más conectado de lo que sabíamos."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7150
translate spanish fangsqandadone_79d7ccee:

    # Fa "When Ivy saw you on the list of people of interest, she took matters into her own hands."
    Fa "Cuando Ivy te vio en la lista de personas de interés, tomó cartas en el asunto."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7154
translate spanish fangsqandadone_4a37218f:

    # Fa "Anyway...I recommend you sleep over this."
    Fa "De todos modos... te recomiendo que te acuestes con esto."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7155
translate spanish fangsqandadone_667b8762:

    # Fa "You've had a long day, and I bet you will still have doubts and questions."
    Fa "Has tenido un largo día, y apuesto a que seguirás teniendo dudas y preguntas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7156
translate spanish fangsqandadone_61936dbd:

    # Fa "Come the morning, you should head back."
    Fa "Por la mañana, deberías volver."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7157
translate spanish fangsqandadone_7b9d6f5a:

    # Fa "I'm heading on a mission to scout a place we may have to attack soon."
    Fa "Me dirijo a una misión para explorar un lugar que quizá tengamos que atacar pronto."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7158
translate spanish fangsqandadone_d0ee6f50:

    # Z "What kind of place?"
    Z "¿Qué tipo de lugar?"

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7161
translate spanish fangsqandadone_97045931:

    # Fa "I told you: I don't trust you just yet. You don't need to know."
    Fa "Ya te lo he dicho: No confío en ti todavía. No necesitas saberlo."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7162
translate spanish fangsqandadone_01b36762:

    # Fa "All I can tell you is that Zeta is not our only concern, and that this particular case does not involve the city, or any of the people dear to you."
    Fa "Todo lo que puedo decirte es que Zeta no es nuestra única preocupación, y que este caso concreto no implica a la ciudad, ni a ninguna de las personas que te son queridas."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7163
translate spanish fangsqandadone_63f6c12a:

    # Fa "Let's just say it's a neighbourly disagreement.."
    Fa "Digamos que es un desacuerdo de vecinos.."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7166
translate spanish fangsqandadone_29f92b37:

    # Fa "So, go home tomorrow. We will keep in touch."
    Fa "Así que, vete a casa mañana. Nos mantendremos en contacto."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7169
translate spanish fangsqandadone_ea2ffc63:

    # Fa "Goodbye for now, Stalker."
    Fa "Adiós por ahora, Acechador."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7172
translate spanish fangsqandadone_c1a3d0a5:

    # Fa "Also..."
    Fa "Además..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7175
translate spanish fangsqandadone_36fb9002:

    # Fa "Next time, when you swing your meat in front of my face..."
    Fa "La próxima vez, cuando balancees tu carne delante de mi cara..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7176
translate spanish fangsqandadone_6e17f9b8:

    # Fa "Don't hesitate so much."
    Fa "No vaciles tanto."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7179
translate spanish fangsqandadone_622621bb:

    # Fa "I can be nice... if I want to."
    Fa "Puedo ser agradable... si quiero."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7183
translate spanish fangsqandadone_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7187
translate spanish fangsqandadone_cb2a17f2:

    # "{i}After a while, you settle down to sleep."
    "{i}Después de un rato, te acomodas para dormir."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7188
translate spanish fangsqandadone_e2be10ff:

    # "{i}In the morning, you swiftly collect your things and make ready to find your way home. Before leaving, you can't help but notice a slim dagger pinned on your bedpost, inches away from your head."
    "{i}Por la mañana, recoges rápidamente tus cosas y te preparas para encontrar el camino a casa. Antes de salir, no puedes evitar fijarte en una delgada daga clavada en el poste de tu cama, a centímetros de tu cabeza."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7189
translate spanish fangsqandadone_c85e769d:

    # "{i}The note it holds reads: I am putting a lot of trust in you, Stalker. Remember however: you know where we live, and I know where your family lives."
    "{i}La nota que contiene dice: Confío mucho en ti, Acechador. Sin embargo, recuerda: tú sabes dónde vivimos, y yo sé dónde vive tu familia."

# game/scripts/day5.rpy:7190
translate spanish fangsqandadone_438a0d50:

